”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”

skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
The Runner Online Alexa skill provides convenient CSUB student news coverage by highlighting pressing stories and previewing the student led laboratory newspaper published bi-weekly, in conjunction with the Department of Communications at California State University, Bakersfield. 
Alexa skill created by multimedia reporter Carlos Hernandez of The Runner.
For more in depth content visit www.therunneronline.com
